=================================================================================

1) Ansible
2) Monitoring
3) SRE[Alias name for DevOps in Google] > Site reliability Engineer

DevOps: All about improvement in existing system

SRE: If their is any problem fix that problem and implement DevOps
Link: https://orangematter.solarwinds.com/2022/03/22/what-is-site-reliability-engineering-sre/
https://www.sketchbubble.com/en/presentation-site-reliability-engineering.html

DevOps Principles:
==================
 Development Team
 Operation Team

1) Development team should respect Operation team.
2) Operation team should respect development team
3) Process should be uniform.
4) IAC[Infrastucture as code]
5) CICD pipeline


SRE Principles
==============
1) Do automation
2) Eliminate manual work.


Killer koda Ansible session: https://killercoda.com/het-tanis/course/Ansible-Labs

Important point: Ansible Configuration are mostly done linux.

Step1: Created servers[4 server in our case, name is server1, server2, server3 and server4]

Step2: Make 1 server as controller

Step3: Creating server group

